This directory contains sample responses from LiteLLM requests for testing the tool blocking plugin.

## OpenAI Format Samples

Files prefixed with `openai_` contain OpenAI-format responses:

**Non-streaming:**
- `openai_text_response.json` - Text-only response (no tool calls)
- `openai_tool_call_response.json` - Single tool call
- `openai_multiple_tool_call_response.json` - Multiple tool calls

**Streaming:**
- `openai_streaming_text_response` - Streaming text-only response
- `openai_streaming_tool_call_response` - Streaming with single tool call
- `openai_streaming_multiple_tool_call_response` - Streaming with multiple tool calls

## Anthropic Format Samples

Files prefixed with `anthropic_` contain real Anthropic-format responses from Claude:

- `anthropic_text_response.json` - Text-only response (no tool calls)
- `anthropic_tool_call_response.json` - Single tool use
- `anthropic_multiple_tool_call_response.json` - Multiple tool uses

**Streaming:**
- `anthropic_streaming_text_response` - Streaming text-only response
- `anthropic_streaming_tool_call_response` - Streaming with single tool call
- `anthropic_streaming_multiple_tool_call_response` - Streaming with multiple tool calls
